        "question": "若等差数列 $\\{a_{n}\\}$ 及正整数 $m$ ($m \\geq 3$) 满足：$a_{1} = 1$，$a_{m} = 2$，且 $\\frac{1}{a_{1}a_{2}} + \\frac{1}{a_{2}a_{3}} + \\dots + \\frac{1}{a_{m-1}a_{m}} = 3$，则 $a_{1} + a_{2} + \\dots + a_{m}$ 的值为______。",
        "solution": [
            "设 $\\{a_{n}\\}$ 的公差为 $d$，则",
            "$\\frac{1}{a_{1}a_{2}} + \\frac{1}{a_{2}a_{3}} + \\dots + \\frac{1}{a_{m-1}a_{m}} = \\sum_{i=1}^{m-1} \\frac{a_{i+1} - a_{i}}{da_{i}a_{i+1}}$",
            "$= \\frac{1}{d} \\sum_{i=1}^{m-1} (\\frac{1}{a_{i}} - \\frac{1}{a_{i+1}}) = \\frac{1}{d}(\\frac{1}{a_{1}} - \\frac{1}{a_{m}}) = \\frac{a_{m} - a_{1}}{da_{1}a_{m}} = \\frac{m-1}{a_{1}a_{m}}$",
            "结合条件可知 $3 = \\frac{m-1}{2}$，得 $m = 7$",
            "所以 $a_{1} + a_{2} + \\dots + a_{m} = \\frac{(1 + 2) \\times 7}{2} = \\frac{21}{2}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\frac{21}{2}$"],
